Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 100th Weekly Dose of Optimism.
The Big 1-0-0.=20
Each week, Packy and I are share 5 stories that make us more optimistic abo=
ut the future. We=E2=80=99ve done it 100 times now =E2=80=94 which means 50=
0+ examples of humans doing cool shit, pushing frontiers, and learning new =
things. There=E2=80=99s not been a slow week throughout the last 100 =E2=80=
=94 we humans are prolific and, seemingly, have become even more prolific i=
n just the last two years. Optimism compounds and progress steadily arcs up=
 and to the right.
We appreciate you all reading and sharing the Weekly Dose over these last 1=
00 editions. We write it, in part, because doing so makes us keep our finge=
r on the pulse of everything happening in science, energy, and technology. =
But we also write the Weekly Dose as a counterbalance to the pessimism that=
 has permeated the mainstream media. Obviously we have much work to do on t=
hat front, but this is our little weekly contribution.
