ifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] teamed up on a Not Boring=
 piece called Gassing the Miracle Machine [ https://substack.com/redirect/8=
4baebad-7466-4ebc-a854-c96f0c29fbdd?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNua=
MZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] on the various ways people were working to re=
invent the =E2=80=9CMiracle Machine,=E2=80=9D the complex system that produ=
ces scientific progress. One of the ways they discussed was the creation of=
 new institutions for research outside of the university, including Arc.=20
Founded by Silvana Konermann, Patrick Hsu, and Patrick Collison after the t=
hree had worked on Fast Grants during COVID, Arc =E2=80=9Cgives scientists =
